Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,882)\pos(1196,432)}愛麗耶絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,882)\pos(1164.6,491.2)}盧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,882)\pos(1163,553.6)}札克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,帶著螢光真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,調查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:03:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,它喊好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哎  剛剛是小福妮的聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  改良過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,做什麼沒價值的改良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,評判是好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那是按誰的標準啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,彼方?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是我吃過所有美食合在一起的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定誇大其詞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就叫它糖果草吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,收集下這附近長的  給大家都嚐嚐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  真噠好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃多少了啊  愛麗耶絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,札克啊  也來吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,口氣別跟我媽似的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你們快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那是衛星嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次看到這麼激動人心的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙真太偉大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這個仙人球裡面果然都是水
